{"type":"message","id":"2fe9c4aa","parentId":"0a2d4d7c","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:13:35.928Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cGPxyS0hCqrR6EnOJthCVCmP","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md","offset":1,"limit":240,"file_path":"~/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/skills/clawhub/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":690,"output":270,"cacheRead":45056,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46016,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774487529079,"responseId":"resp_02cdc5ebace3cbbd0169c4883b7c388191a15297b4e077458e"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3f7d65f5","parentId":"2fe9c4aa","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:13:35.944Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cGPxyS0hCqrR6EnOJthCVCmP","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: clawhub\ndescription: Use the ClawHub CLI to search, install, update, and publish agent skills from clawhub.com. Use when you need to fetch new skills on the fly, sync installed skills to latest or a specific version, or publish new/updated skill folders with the npm-installed clawhub CLI.\nmetadata:\n  {\n    \"openclaw\":\n      {\n        \"requires\": { \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"] },\n        \"install\":\n          [\n            {\n              \"id\": \"node\",\n              \"kind\": \"node\",\n              \"package\": \"clawhub\",\n              \"bins\": [\"clawhub\"],\n              \"label\": \"Install ClawHub CLI (npm)\",\n            },\n          ],\n      },\n  }\n---\n\n# ClawHub CLI\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nnpm i -g clawhub\n```\n\nAuth (publish)\n\n```bash\nclawhub login\nclawhub whoami\n```\n\nSearch\n\n```bash\nclawhub search \"postgres backups\"\n```\n\nInstall\n\n```bash\nclawhub install my-skill\nclawhub install my-skill --version 1.2.3\n```\n\nUpdate (hash-based match + upgrade)\n\n```bash\nclawhub update my-skill\nclawhub update my-skill --version 1.2.3\nclawhub update --all\nclawhub update my-skill --force\nclawhub update --all --no-input --force\n```\n\nList\n\n```bash\nclawhub list\n```\n\nPublish\n\n```bash\nclawhub publish ./my-skill --slug my-skill --name \"My Skill\" --version 1.2.0 --changelog \"Fixes + docs\"\n```\n\nNotes\n\n- Default registry: https://clawhub.com (override with CLAWHUB_REGISTRY or --registry)\n- Default workdir: cwd (falls back to OpenClaw workspace); install dir: ./skills (override with --workdir / --dir / CLAWHUB_WORKDIR)\n- Update command hashes local files, resolves matching version, and upgrades to latest unless --version is set\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774487615939}}
{"type":"message","id":"45a94b86","parentId":"3f7d65f5","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:16:02.673Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 你是想要 **装/找 polyclaw 这个技能**，对吧？\n\n我可以直接帮你查，但按你之前定的规矩，**装任何技能前我会先走 `skill-vetter` 做安全审查**。  \n现在有两种走法：\n\n1. **先搜 polyclaw 技能**\n   - 我帮你查 ClawHub 上有没有、叫什么、描述是啥\n\n2. **直接准备安装**\n   - 我先搜\n   - 再用 `skill-vetter` 过一遍\n   - 没明显风险再装\n\n你如果是这个意思，直接回我一句：\n- `搜 polyclaw`\n或\n- `安装 polyclaw`\n\n如果你说的不是技能，而是别的 “polyclaw”，我也可以先帮你确认是哪个。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":715,"output":190,"cacheRead":45568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":46473,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774487615945,"responseId":"resp_04e7f81f78613cfd0169c488ce31bc8191b3d1398681d18e3a"}}
