{"type":"message","id":"ba695d2e","parentId":"81db76e5","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:23:31.186Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Structuring the response**\n\nI think categorizing the information will help clarify things for the user. It might also be a good idea to ask if they want a more detailed audit of each category. I’m curious about what their preferences are and how I can better assist them. Keeping it organized could lead to a more helpful and tailored response. Let’s ensure I’m addressing their needs effectively!\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 我现在能用的技能不少，按用途给你过一遍：\n\n**飞书 / 协作**\n- `feishu-channel-rules`\n- `feishu-im-read`\n- `feishu-troubleshoot`\n\n**技能管理 / 诊断**\n- `clawhub`：搜、装、更新技能\n- `skill-vetter`：装技能前做安全审查\n- `skill-creator`：创建、整理、审查技能\n- `mcporter`：管 MCP server / tools\n- `node-connect`：排查节点连接问题\n- `healthcheck`：主机安全和巡检\n\n**通用信息类**\n- `weather`\n- `web-search-pro`\n- `humanizer-zh`\n\n**X / Twitter**\n- `xurl`\n\n**OKX / 链上**\n- `okx-agentic-wallet`\n- `okx-dex-market`\n- `okx-dex-signal`\n- `okx-dex-swap`\n- `okx-dex-token`\n- `okx-dex-trenches`\n- `okx-onchain-gateway`\n- `okx-security`\n- `okx-wallet-portfolio`\n\n如果你说的“检查”是这几种意思，我都能继续：\n\n1. **列出我当前已安装技能的完整清单**\n2. **检查哪些技能可用、哪些坏了**\n3. **把每个技能是干嘛的详细解释一遍**\n4. **给所有技能做一次安全/可用性巡检**\n\n你要是想来真的，我下一步可以直接帮你做：\n- **可用性检查**\n- **安全审查**\n- **按用途整理成清单**\n\n你回我一句：`做全量巡检`，我就开始。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":46946,"output":834,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47780,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774487795805,"responseId":"resp_03525c7a724839100169c48a847618819184434f667436af67"}}
