{"type":"message","id":"6797acd8","parentId":"6b01f1fa","timestamp":"2026-03-26T01:27:56.987Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Interpreting user inquiry**\n\nI see the user is asking about a message that translates to \"What about this?\" and it seems they're inquiring about the polyclaw skill status. I should clarify that this isn't coming from me. The quoted message indicates that polyclaw is installed and usable but in a read-only manner, without integration as an OpenClaw skill. It might be helpful to check the actual workspace, but I think I can answer without needing any tools.\n\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 这个回复的意思是：\n\n**polyclaw 本体基本已经跑起来了**，但现在还只是 **只读阶段**。\n\n翻成人话就是：\n\n- **已经能用**\n  - `uv` 装好了\n  - `uv sync` 跑完了\n  - 只读命令测通了\n  - 像 `markets trending --limit 5` 这种查市场的命令已经有返回\n\n- **现在能做的**\n  - 看热门盘\n  - 搜市场\n  - 查某个 market 详情\n  - 总之是“看数据、查信息”这类只读操作\n\n- **现在还不能安全下单**\n  - 还**没配私钥**\n  - 还**没做 wallet approve**\n  - 还**没碰真钱交易**\n\n所以这条消息不是“挂了”，也不是“没装好”，而是：\n\n**装好了，读数据没问题；交易功能还没开。**\n\n如果你想，我下一步可以直接帮你判断两件事里的一个：\n\n1. **它只是 CLI 能跑，还是已经真正接成 OpenClaw 技能了**\n2. **直接用 polyclaw 给你看热门市场 / 搜市场**\n\n你要的话我可以马上帮你查一句最关键的：  \n**“现在这个 polyclaw，到底是命令行能用，还是已经变成我可直接调用的技能？”**"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1160,"output":510,"cacheRead":46848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":48518,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774488249275,"responseId":"resp_081a8259123729420169c48b93dd888191b6d184eeb4ead445"}}
