{"type":"message","id":"2ce63457","parentId":"d2638550","timestamp":"2026-03-26T04:05:38.360Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 好了，已经起来了。\n\n我刚查了：\n- `Feishu` 状态是 **ON / OK**\n- 当前这个直聊 session 也在\n- `openclaw status` 能正常返回\n\n所以 gateway 现在是活的。  \n你要的话，我下一步可以继续帮你看 **polyclaw 为什么还没进技能列表**。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":742,"output":87,"cacheRead":53760,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":54589,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774497929494,"responseId":"resp_074081bf1bbe73780169c4b08f95d08191822ef83d8f84bcf7"}}
