{"type":"message","id":"60948280","parentId":"16f917b4","timestamp":"2026-03-26T04:10:37.109Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"我再补一刀，查一下 OpenClaw 的技能路径/配置是不是只扫某几个目录。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_MMk75KWpeoZdZAAKlJZBIUO8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"set -e\nprintf '== openclaw help refs ==\\n'\n(openclaw help 2>/dev/null || true) | grep -Ei \"skill|skills\" | sed -n '1,80p'\nprintf '\\n== config files mentioning skills ==\\n'\ngrep -RIn \"skills\" ~/.openclaw --exclude-dir=.git 2>/dev/null | sed -n '1,160p'\nprintf '\\n== docs mentioning ~/.openclaw/skills ==\\n'\ngrep -RIn \"~/.openclaw/skills\\|extensions/openclaw\\|available_skills\" /home/zbb/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs /home/zbb/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw 2>/dev/null | sed -n '1,200p'","workdir":"/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace","yieldMs":10000,"timeout":90,"pty":false,"ask":"on-miss"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":832,"output":579,"cacheRead":56320,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57731,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774498212363,"responseId":"resp_0925ced023c1fc130169c4b1b432b88191af650fa62b1032a3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f751cd2b","parentId":"60948280","timestamp":"2026-03-26T04:10:47.130Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_MMk75KWpeoZdZAAKlJZBIUO8","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Command still running (session kind-kelp, pid 2547496). Use process (list/poll/log/write/kill/clear/remove) for follow-up."}],"details":{"status":"running","sessionId":"kind-kelp","pid":2547496,"startedAt":1774498237115,"cwd":"/home/zbb/.openclaw/workspace","tail":"dules/openclaw/docs/concepts/agent-workspace.md:133:- `~/.openclaw/skills/` (managed skills)\n/home/zbb/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:920:    Use managed overrides instead of editing the repo copy. Put your changes in `~/.openclaw/skills/<name>/SKILL.md` (or add a folder via `skills.load.extraDirs` in `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json`). Precedence is `<workspace>/skills` > `~/.openclaw/skills` > bundled, so managed overrides win without touching git. Only upstream-worthy edits should live in the repo and go out as PRs.\n/home/zbb/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:924:    Yes. Add extra directories via `skills.load.extraDirs` in `~/.openclaw/openclaw.json` (lowest precedence). Default precedence remains: `<workspace>/skills` → `~/.openclaw/skills` → bundled → `skills.load.extraDirs`. `clawhub` installs into `./skills` by default, which OpenClaw treats as `<workspace>/skills` on the next session.\n/home/zbb/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:1043:    3. Override the skill metadata (workspace or `~/.openclaw/skills`) to allow Linux:\n/home/zbb/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:1080:    Native installs land in the active workspace `skills/` directory. For shared skills across agents, place them in `~/.openclaw/skills/<name>/SKILL.md`. Some skills expect binaries installed via Homebrew; on Linux that means Linuxbrew (see the Homebrew Linux FAQ entry above). See [Skills](/tools/skills) and [ClawHub](/tools/clawhub).\n/home/zbb/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/help/faq.md:1244:      and shared skills (`~/.openclaw/skills`).\n/home/zbb/.nvm/versions/node/v24.14.0/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/zh-CN/tools/clawhub.md:55:默认情况下，CLI 会将 Skills 安装到当前工作目录下的 `./skills`。如果已配置 OpenClaw 工作区，`clawhub` 会回退到该工作区，除非你通过 `--workdir`（或 `CLAWHUB_WORKDIR`）进行覆盖。OpenClaw 从 `<workspace>/skills` 加载工作区 Skills，并会在**下一个**会话中生效。如果你已经在使用 `~"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774498247125}}
